.TH tga2paa 1 "February 2026" "arma-tools" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
tga2paa \- convert TGA textures to PAA/PAC
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B tga2paa
.RI [ flags ]
.I input.tga
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B tga2paa
converts TGA files to PAA/PAC and validates power-of-two dimensions.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI "-o " path
Output PAA/PAC path.
.TP
.BI "-format " fmt
Compression format:
.B auto
(default),
.BR dxt1 ,
.BR dxt3 ,
.BR dxt5 .
.TP
.BR -h , " --help"
Show help.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR paa2tga (1),
.BR paa2img (1)
